<br>
Foil -- what most people thing of as fencing with a very flexible thing blade.  Points are scored through 'touches' of the tip to the valid target region (essentially a V of the torso)<br>
<br>
Saber -- slightly curved blade with a pommel designed to be used as a slicing weapon.  points are scored by 'cutting' touches of the edge of the blade to a much larger section of the opponent.  A more elegant weapon the saber is capable of scoring points, for examples, from a sly riposte that touchs the sleeve of the opponent.<br>
<br>
Epee -- a sturdier version of the foil.  A much heavier weapon and a style that allows points to be scored almost anywhere. (touch to the toe counts for example)   The Epee doesnt really bend and has significant mementum behind it, this makes it a much more dangerous fencing weapon as it has a heightened risk of blunt truama if it were to strike the throat or other vulernable areas.  Epee is a much more agressive weapon .  <p>Qhue Oculorum, Master Scholar and High Enchanter of Tunare</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showMessageRange?topicID=19474.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b> <a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showMessageRange?topicID=19474.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showMessageRange?topicID=19474.topic&start=61&stop=64>4</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showPrevMessage?topicID=19474.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showNextMessage?topicID=19474.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=19474.topic&index=40><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.emailToFriend?topicID=19474.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.threadControl?topicID=19474.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic 